  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Quora?",
  "response": "Quora is an American question-and-answer website where users can ask questions and receive answers from other users. The name \"Quora\" is derived from the word \"quorum,\" which refers to the minimum number of members required to be present at a meeting to make the proceedings valid. In the context of the website, Quora represents a platform where a community of users come together to share and exchange knowledge, effectively forming a \"quorum\" of information and insights.",
